Well, we were able to
figure out Jared's age.

00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:03.800
It is 8.

00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:06.465
It is 3 times Jared's age.

00:02:06.465 --> 00:02:08.090
If you know your
multiplication tables,

00:02:08.090 --> 00:02:09.810
this should maybe
jump out at you.

00:02:09.810 --> 00:02:12.700
And your multiplication tables
really are one of those things

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:16.192
in mathematics that you should
really just know back and forth

00:02:16.192 --> 00:02:18.150
just because it will make
the rest of your life

00:02:18.150 --> 00:02:20.090
very, very, very simple.

00:02:20.090 --> 00:02:23.620
